### Assign player to team
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/academy/team-assignments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "player_id": "{{playerId}}",
  "team_id": "{{teamId}}",
  "start_date": "2026-07-08"
}

### Mark assignment primary
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/academy/team-assignments/{{assignmentId}}/primary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Finalize assignment
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/academy/team-assignments/{{assignmentId}}/finalize
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List player assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/academy/team-assignments/players/{{playerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
